node.text:
This spectacular 1.6 acre property rests high above the glistening waters of the Long Island Sound and Larchmont Harbor, with over 500 ft of private shoreline, a deep water dock, a jetty, and an area for swimming or launching a small watercraft. Magnificently sited on a lush promontory adjacent to Manor Park, this beautiful 8,182 SF, 1898 Victorian is designed to highlight the gorgeous panoramas from every room. Experience unobstructed views from the wraparound porch, bluestone patio, in-ground pool & spa. An original stable is now a 3 bed, 2 bath guest house with chic-retro kitchen. At the heart of this 3-level turreted icon is a great room that soars 2 stories with stairway to a glass cupola. Each space melds period grandeur with glamour. This home is unrivaled.
25 Park Avenue, Larchmont, NY $11,300,000
7 Bedrooms
6/2 Baths
Don’t miss out on the opportunity to own this extraordinary waterfront home, listed with @Mimi.Magarelli. Learn more via the link below.
https://wpsir.co/25ParkAvenue
